FBIS3-36944 "drsov028_d_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-028 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Feb 1994 Regional Affairs Tambov Chief Criticizes Bureaucrats, Resigns MK0902133094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 9 Feb 94 p 2 MK0902133094 Moscow SEGODNYA Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report under the "Provincial Chronicle" rubric: "Tambov"] [Text] The Russian Federation president's representative in Tambov Oblast has said he has decided to resign because "a bureaucratic coup is being staged in the country, bureaucrats have seized power, and the president has been deprived of the ability to govern." He believes that the oblast is sliding into an economic abyss, because industry and the agricultural sector are headed by people who are "unable to work under market conditions."
